criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Gestational age < 35 weeks;

          -  Diagnosed as neonatal respiratory distress syndrome;

          -  Inhalation of atmospheric conditions, blood oxygen partial pressure (PaO2) <6.7kPa

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Neonatal respiratory distress syndrome Grade Ⅳ(White Lung);

          -  Hypercapnia（pH<7.20, PaCO2﹥8.0kPa);

          -  Respiratory malformations or Complexity of congenital heart disease;

          -  Severe circulatory dysfunction
